content:
In Spring '25, Salesforce stops supporting OmniStudio components in unlocked packages. Make sure that you remove OmniStudio components with unlocked packages from your deployment pipelines.

This change applies to Salesforce Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions where OmniStudio is enabled.

See Metadata Coverage for the list of supported OmniStudio components.

Salesforce DX Developer Guide: Unlocked Packages
title: Remove OmniStudio Components from Unlocked Packages
